de: Addendum No 1 to Project Agreement between Switzerland represented by the Swiss State Secretariat for Economic Affairs (seco) and the Republic of Poland represented by the Ministry of Regional Development as the National Coordination Unit (NCU) concerning the Grant for the Project KIK-41 "Renewable Energy Systems: Niepolomice, Wieliczka, Skawina and Miechów"  - 04-02-2013 - Abkommen zwischen der Schweiz, vertreten durch das SECO, und Polen, vertreten durch das Ministerium für regionale Entwicklung, bezüglich der Förderung erneuerbarer Energiequellen in der Region Niepolomice, Wieliczka, Skawina und Klaj, KIK-41
en: Addendum No 1 to Project Agreement between Switzerland represented by the Swiss State Secretariat for Economic Affairs (seco) and the Republic of Poland represented by the Ministry of Regional Development as the National Coordination Unit (NCU) concerning the Grant for the Project KIK-41 "Renewable Energy Systems: Niepolomice, Wieliczka, Skawina and Miechów"  - 04-02-2013 - Project Agreement between Switzerland represented by the Swiss State Secretariat for Economic Affairs (seco) and the Republic of Poland represented by the Ministry of Regional Development as the National Coordination Unit (NCU) concerning the Grant for the Project KIK-41 "Renewable Energy Systems: Niepolomice, Wieliczka, Skawina and Klaj"
